  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249340/extras/91b9fb644941d7731c3a65540d823c87.avif?t=1743903227\" width=605 height=115 /></span><br>Name your company and start your very first business!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249340/extras/6e811bbe2b1f102346ad0e74d61592a2.avif?t=1743903227\" width=600 height=434 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249340/extras/f6a8ca35b4b34703ece48dee61700ab4.avif?t=1743903227\" width=605 height=115 /></span><br>Be a good boss, hire talents with the most reasonable salary during the interview, and build the startup team!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249340/extras/474c85ca449f91204ae27221781623c1.avif?t=1743903227\" width=600 height=340 /></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249340/extras/0c78de95a225435453b8dba14366d920.avif?t=1743903227\" width=605 height=115 /></span><br>Your employees have needs or ideas when working, keep them in a good mood!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249340/extras/75ced80ad8674179a5e1e87018980caf.avif?t=1743903227\" width=600 height=434 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Cultivate employees and make everyone a boss</h2>Everyone has the ambition to advance their career. Train your employees and raise their stats.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249340/extras/25c7d8a020cc5b3fd43cd330aa5595e5.avif?t=1743903227\" width=600 height=436 /></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249340/extras/b4facafb919c3d804283d80d10ef0e18.avif?t=1743903227\" width=605 height=115 /></span><br>A website needs server! Buy server rooms in various cities and regions; keep them running but not overheating!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249340/extras/9bea2a2f1bf1265c0ea5190e7d42c71b.avif?t=1743903227\" width=600 height=402 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249340/extras/c9780b8f7f775993d584ff93853df8e2.avif?t=1743903227\" width=605 height=115 /></span><br>Don't do it for free! With enough users, your website will generate lots of page views. Don't let them go to waste; sign advertisement contracts for considerable income. The more the merrier! But too many ads will also lower user satisfaction. It's up to you to keep the balance.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2249340/extras/89644b360ae26ec640f91b9cc752a8a6.avif?t=1743903227\" width=600 height=360 /></span>",
